text: Stanisław Wierzbicki was a rower from Poland. Wierzbicki competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics. He was born on 13 May 1959 and died on 10 December 2018.Stanisław Wierzbicki == References == Category:1959 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Polish rowers Category:Olympians for Poland
title: Stanisław Wierzbicki
